schema.description:
This is the schema to extract.

Examples:
1. To extract object properties, you can use the following schema:
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "name": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "age": {
      "type": "number"
    }
  }
}
```

